        <name>XDfePrach_SelfTestExample</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para>This example runs the DFE Prach device using the driver APIs. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>The example goes through the following steps:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Create and system initialize the device driver instance.</para></listitem><listitem><para>Read SW and HW version numbers.</para></listitem><listitem><para>Reset the device.</para></listitem><listitem><para>Configure the device.</para></listitem><listitem><para>Initialize the device.</para></listitem><listitem><para>Activate the device.</para></listitem><listitem><para>Deactivate the device.</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para><para><simplesect kind="return"><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS if the example has completed successfully.</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_FAILURE if the example has failed.//! [testexample1] </para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
